e fight over the planes when you could be having 2 in 1 day ... dunno but itjust occured to me when we did it a week ago... why doesnt someone hold mourning plane raids and someone later that night hold one too? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uveladorn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Veladorn</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Grinning Gargoyle</span><br>  Posts: 653<br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/14/01 4:51:39 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://yourpage.blazenet.net/anabelle/triad/valas3.jpg width=136 hieght=200></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: why dont people do this...</span><hr size=1> It has been done and usually it causes fights because one group complains that the other did not leave early enough or killed respawn, etc.<br>
